title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: You may unceremoniously run out of patience and want immediate change. However, your sudden involvement in an unusual pursuit might shock longtime friends and associates as rebellious Uranus opposes the brooding Scorpio Sun in your 5th House of Spontaneity. Others may not realize that your current makeover is the result of lingering desires that you no longer wish to suppress. Embrace experiences that beckon you now while continuing to integrate disparate elements of your being. Give yourself permission to diverge from expectations in order to converge on an authentic expression of who you are. Transformation takes time. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
